-- MOVES-J.C. Flowers hires Mead Park founder David Moffitt - NYT
-- 
-- Wed Sep 10, 2014 09:19AM EDT
-- None



Sept 10 (Reuters) - David Moffitt, one of the founders of hedge fund Mead Park Management, will join private equity firm J.C. Flowers & Co LLC, according to a memo obtained by the New York Times.

Moffitt will head a new platform, which will involve buying fixed-income assets, the paper reported. (http://nyti.ms/1AyfgDz) These investments would include portfolios of loans to small and midsize businesses, and commercial and residential real estate, the paper reported, citing a person familiar with the matter.